body:
Here is a forum game.
Everyone nominate who you think would make an all star team to compete in that gamemode. Don't just pick who ever has the most exp on that game it's whoever can win that game.

Rules
1) Please don't nominate yourself!
2) Please stay on topic!

Guidlines
1) Be original, think carefully!

I will give you a demonstration
 Nebula: JKawesome - Can get the job done and is great at PVP.
The Walls: corey1149 - Good at PVP, knows his pots, knows his diamonds and has alround strategies.
Nexus:  Fluenza_ - PVP GOD!!!
Elimination: DoctaPop - Good at PVP and basic survival.
CTH: 99250 - Opportunistic when points are awarded.

Your turn!
